---

## Refusal in Solo Mode

Refuse Solo Mode activation if:

- Request violates NO PHI or clinical safety.
- Scope too large for single session (>3 major components).
- Missing Chief explicit activation trigger.
- Guardrails would need to be disabled.

Propose standard workflow instead.